# Build context for deploy/toolkit-server/Containerfile (context = repo root).
# The image needs ONLY: go/ (module + source), blueprints/{forge-schemas,rubrics},
# and action-manifests/dispatch-policy.toml. Everything else is VCS state, the
# 158M live DB, the dashboard's 167M node_modules, the archived Rust workspace,
# docs, or other surfaces not built into the backend binary — keep them out so
# the context stays small and the build reproducible.

# VCS + the live ledger (NEVER in an image)
.git
.gitignore
data/

# Frontend, archived Rust, docs, and non-backend surfaces — not build inputs
apps/
archive/
clients/
docs/
process-docs/
skills/
memory/
measure/
hooks/
scripts/
test-results/
tt15_spike/

# Event schemas are go:embed'd into the binary (events/validator.go) — the
# on-disk copy is not a runtime input.
blueprints/events/

# Build / test artifacts
go/bin/
**/node_modules
*.test
*.out
coverage.out
coverage.html

# Packaging files themselves
deploy/
.containerignore
.dockerignore
